items.name: FIT_TO_WINDOW
desc: specifies that the video should be zoomed to window size

items.name: FIT_TO_WINDOW_FIXED_ASPECT
desc: specifies that the video should be zoomed to window size with using a fixed aspect ratio

items.name: FULLSCREEN
desc: specifies that the video should be displayed in fullscreen mode, if available

items.name: NOT_AVAILABLE
desc: specifies that the video window itself is not available at all, e.g.
in cases of pure audio playback

items.name: ORIGINAL
desc: specifies that the video should be displayed with its original size

items.name: ZOOM_1_TO_2
desc: specifies that the video should be zoomed to a factor of 1:2

items.name: ZOOM_1_TO_4
desc: specifies that the video should be zoomed to a factor of 1:4

items.name: ZOOM_2_TO_1
desc: specifies that the video should be zoomed to a factor of 2:1

items.name: ZOOM_4_TO_1
desc: specifies that the video should be zoomed to a factor of 4:1
